think about the tool-assisted
hunting at Fongoli

00:19:07.800 --> 00:19:09.730
it perhaps can tell us more about

00:19:09.730 --> 00:19:12.900
some of the early hominin
hunting that went on

00:19:12.900 --> 00:19:17.410
